snippet.title: Real World Police
snippet.description:
Real World Police is an investigative video news program covering US law enforcement & crime. We publish original reporting and exclusive footage, routinely scooping traditional media outlets on major stories.

In just over two years, Real World Police has published more than 700 impactful videos, attracting a cumulative watch time of more than 50 million hours and a daily audience larger than the circulation of The New York Times.

Real World Police is produced by Jay Horowitz and published by Real World Media.

Committed to ethical journalism. Biased in favor of the truth.

Impersonating a journalist @ rwp.yt/hi

~~~

Do you have *nonpublic* information on a story we are or should be covering? Email tips@rwp.yt.

We don't publish footage that has already been published elsewhere unless we have significant new footage and information to add. Please don't send news articles.

Found an error? Email corrections@rwp.yt.

~~~

Comments are moderated: Be relevant. Be real. Be reasonable.
